org.apache.nutch.fetcher

Class FetchItemQueues

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.nutch.fetcher.FetchItemQueues

  • public class FetchItemQueues
extends java.lang.Object
    Convenience class - a collection of queues that keeps track of the total number of items, and provides items eligible for fetching from any queue.
